title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 50-4.2 - Definition
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 50-4.2 - Definition

State Regulations

For the purpose of this Subpart, personal health-related information means any information concerning the health of a person which identifies or could reasonably be used to identify a person. Notes
